org.apache.ambari.server.state.alert

Class AggregateDefinitionMapping

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.apache.ambari.server.state.alert.AggregateDefinitionMapping

  • public class AggregateDefinitionMapping
extends Object
    The AggregateDefinitionMapping is used to keep an in-memory mapping of all of the AlertDefinitions that have aggregate definitions associated with them.
